644
00:48:56,257 --> 00:48:57,368
Isn't that right?

645
00:49:03,198 --> 00:49:04,087
Why?

646
00:49:04,204 --> 00:49:06,753
This is my mom's room so of course she's in there.

647
00:49:06,832 --> 00:49:07,926
So,

648
00:49:08,880 --> 00:49:10,397
