656
00:49:42,112 --> 00:49:44,583
We have a wish.

657
00:49:45,367 --> 00:49:46,491
We?

658
00:49:47,158 --> 00:49:48,819
If you can fulfill that wish for us,

659
00:49:48,924 --> 00:49:52,453
