666
00:50:05,922 --> 00:50:06,967
Pick one.

667
00:50:07,281 --> 00:50:09,307
The choice belongs to the two of you.

668
00:50:09,843 --> 00:50:10,864
- What?
- What?

669
00:50:11,060 --> 00:50:13,073
All our wishes are in here,

670
00:50:13,138 --> 00:50:16,341
